sky.f1.uk.title: 30 Years of the PDC World Champs'
sky.f1.uk.description: In celebration of 30 years of the PDC World Darts Championship, take a look back at the very first tournament, a classic final from 2007 and one of the greatest legs ever played. Ep 1.

sky.f1.uk.title: The Taylor Years
sky.f1.uk.description: Hear from the legendary Phil Taylor as the 16-time world champion recounts his glory years at the PDC World Darts Championship. Ep 2.

sky.f1.uk.title: The Greatest Final 07:Taylor v RVB
sky.f1.uk.description: In the final act at the Circus Tavern, two of the finest players to have ever played the sport created a match for the ages, as Phil Taylor and Raymond van Barneveld met in the final. Ep 3.

sky.f1.uk.title: John Part's Journey 2001-08

sky.f1.uk.title: The Rise Of MVG (2013)

sky.f1.uk.title: Gary Anderson: Back2Back Champion
sky.f1.uk.description: Gary Anderson tells the story of his PDC World Darts Championship triumphs in 2015 and 2016, as the Scotsman become only the third player to win back-to-back titles. Ep 6.

sky.f1.uk.title: Rob Cross: A Year To Remember 2018
sky.f1.uk.description: At the first time of asking, Rob Cross shocked the world on his PDC World Darts Championship debut by defeating the retiring Phil Taylor in the final at Alexandra Palace in 2018. Ep 7.

sky.f1.uk.title: Peter Wright: Double Champ 20 & 22
sky.f1.uk.description: A two-time winner of the coveted Sid Waddell Trophy, Peter 'Snakebite' Wright recounts the highs and lows of PDC World Darts Championship glory. Ep 8.

sky.f1.uk.title: Gerwyn Price: Welsh Glory 2021

sky.f1.uk.title: The Greatest Leg - 2023 Final
sky.f1.uk.description: In 2023, both MVG and Michael Smith were on course to record a nine-dart leg; the Dutchman fell short by a single dart, but the Englishman achieved perfection. Ep 10.

E4Plus1.uk.description: Thorpe Park: After passing his driving test, Simon takes the boys on their first road trip: a day out at Thorpe Park, where Will disgraces himself on the roller coaster. (S1 Ep3/6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: Will Gets a Girlfriend: Will sees that going to a mixed-sex school isn't so bad when he pulls the most popular girl in the year above. But he alienates his hard-won new friends. (S1 Ep4/6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: Caravan Club: The boys call Jay's bluff and go to the Camber Sands meeting of the Caravan Club to see if it really is a massive sex party. Jay's dad gives them advice about sex. (S1 Ep5/6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: Xmas Party: It's the end of term and Will has been voted chairman of the Christmas prom committee, so he ropes in Simon, Jay and Neil to help get things organised. (S1 Ep6/6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sian, who's 24, wants a man to drive her wild, who she can love more than her beloved car. And 33-year-old fashion entrepreneur Tansel is after a woman to settle down with. (S8 Ep5/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox Festive Special
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch top Christmas telly, from Jamie's Easy Christmas to Top Gun: Maverick, First Dates at Christmas, Michael McIntyre's Christmas Wheel and much more.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Promposal: With Closet-Con imminent, Claire's on high alert and convinced there's a company mole. Phil goes vigilante when he and Gloria confront Alice for stealing her recipe. (S7 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Crazy Train: When Dede gets remarried, Manny convinces the family to take the train to the wedding. And Jay's ecstatic that Dede is moving on for good. (S7 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Conjugal Conjecture: The gang face an awkward morning after Sheldon's mother and Leonard's father share an evening together. Penny's family arrive in town. (S10 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Military Miniaturization: Howard has a meeting with Air Force representative Colonel Williams about the gyroscope he invented with Leonard and Sheldon. (S10 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Skinner's Sense of Snow: When a huge snowdrift engulfs the school, Bart leads the kids in a rebellion, gagging Principal Skinner and tying him to a chair as they run amok. (S12 Ep8/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Kill Gil, Volumes I & II: The Simpsons are stuck with an unwanted house guest, Gil, at Christmas. And he stays for a whole year... until Marge throws him out on Christmas Eve. (S18 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Proposal Proposal: Amy must decide whether or not to marry Sheldon and gives him an answer to his proposal. Howard and Bernadette struggle with some unexpected news. (S11 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Retraction Reaction: Leonard angers the university during an embarrassing interview. Amy and Bernadette must hide their success from Sheldon and Howard. (S11 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Relaxation Integration: Amy tries to convince Sheldon that he has a more laid-back side. Raj and Stuart compete to woo Bernadette's new colleague Ruchi. (S11 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Explosion Implosion: Howard and Sheldon bond on a trip to the desert to launch a model rocket. Leonard is annoyed when his mother befriends Penny. (S11 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Collaboration Contamination: Sheldon and Raj ask Bernadette for advice about their jealousy when Amy and Howard decide to collaborate on a new project. (S11 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Proton Regeneration: Sheldon goes head-to-head with Wil Wheaton as they compete for the role of the new Professor Proton when the TV series has a reboot. (S11 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Geology Methodology: Sheldon and Bert collaborate on a research project, but Sheldon feels embarrassed to be associated with the study of geology. (S11 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tesla Recoil: Leonard and Howard learn that Sheldon went to work with the military behind their backs. Bernadette thinks Ruchi's trying to steal her job. (S11 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bitcoin Entanglement: Sheldon seeks revenge when the guys cut him out of a potentially valuable investment. A secret about Leonard and Penny is revealed. (S11 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Confidence Erosion: Sheldon and Amy try to use maths to make their wedding planning less stressful. Raj falls out with Howard. (S11 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Celebration Reverberation: Sheldon and Howard plan birthday celebrations for Amy and Halley. Leonard is stressed by a Christmas letter from his brother. (S11 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Matrimonial Metric: Sheldon and Amy secretly test their friends, to work out who should be best man and maid of honour at their wedding. (S11 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Solo Oscillation: Amy and Leonard bond over some experiments. Bert replaces Howard in his band. Penny gives Sheldon unexpected scientific inspiration. (S11 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Separation Triangulation: Raj gets into a domestic drama with his new date Nell and her estranged husband. Sheldon rents his old room back from Leonard. (S11 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Novelization Correlation: Amy appears on the Professor Proton show. Penny hates the idea that the female protagonist in Leonard's novel is based on her. (S11 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Neonatal Nomenclature: Bernadette's friends try various tactics to help her go into labour. (S11 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Athenaeum Allocation: Leonard jumps through hoops to secure the perfect wedding venue for Sheldon and Amy. Howard and Bernadette face a big decision. (S11 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Gates Excitation: The guys do everything in their power to meet Bill Gates when his firm has dealings with the pharmaceutical company Penny works for. (S11 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tenant Disassociation: Leonard competes with Sheldon to become president of the tenants' association. Howard and Raj find a drone in the back garden. (S11 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Reclusive Potential: A brilliant scientist invites Sheldon to his isolated cabin, and Leonard, Raj and Howard go along for the trip. (S11 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Comet Polarization: Sheldon isn't pleased by the comic book shop's new-found popularity. Raj tries to take the credit for Penny's astronomical discovery. (S11 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Monetary Insufficiency: Sheldon goes to Las Vegas to try to win money for science. Penny and Bernadette take Amy shopping for a wedding dress. (S11 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Sibling Realignment: When Sheldon finds out that his mum won't come to his wedding unless he invites his brother Georgie, he and Leonard head to Texas. (S11 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bow Tie Asymmetry: Everyone is focused on making sure that the arrangements for Amy and Sheldon's big day go according to plan - except the bride and groom. (S11 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Little Mermaid
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2023) Live action remake of the Disney classic with Halle Bailey and Melissa McCarthy. Can mermaid Ariel get a kiss from Prince Eric and keep her legs? Evil Aunt Ursula hopes not.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Finding Father Christmas
E4Plus1.uk.description: A 16-year-old boy (Lenny Rush) goes on a quest to prove his dad wrong and that Father Christmas does exist. A star-studded, heart-warming drama also featuring Greg Davies and Stephen Fry.

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates at Christmas
E4Plus1.uk.description: Martial artists, firefighters and professional princesses are on the festive menu as Fred opens the restaurant doors for singletons hoping to find Christmas romance in their stockings.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: Field Trip: It's a new term at Rudge Park comprehensive: time for the infamous sociology and geography field trip to Swanage... (S2 Ep1/6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: Work Experience: Jay arranges work experience for himself and Simon at his dad's company, but a mix-up leaves Neil at a newspaper and Will at a garage. (S2 Ep2/6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: Will's Birthday: Will plans a suitably grown-up dinner to celebrate his birthday, but his event clashes with a far more popular party, leaving his friends with a dilemma. (S2 Ep3/6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: Night Out in London: Will decides that the lads should be 'the boys who go to clubs'. They head to the West End, meeting aggressive bouncers and angry bus passengers. (S2 Ep4/6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Duke of Edinburgh Awards: Will is asked to co-ordinate the school's Duke of Edinburgh Award scheme and immediately turns the situation to his advantage. (S2 Ep5/6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: End of Term: Will is stressed about exams, Jay has other things on his mind, Simon finally seems to be making headway with Carli, and Neil forgets his kit for his PE exam. (S2 Ep6/6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Spuds: Phil and Claire take Haley and Dylan to dinner to reassure them they're not bad parents. Mitch and Cam chaperone Lily's first date. Jay and Gloria go to Joe's school play. (S11 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Double-Click: Claire can't seem to find the right time to fire an employee, Phil thinks he caught Luke with a girl in his bed, and no one notices that Alex has moved back. (S7 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Tale of Three Cities: There's a reunion after trips took the Dunphys to New York; Mitch, Cam and Lily to the Midwest; and Jay, Gloria, Manny and Joe to Juarez in Mexico. (S8 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: I Won't Be Home for Christmas: When Moe convinces Homer to stay out late on Christmas Eve, Marge kicks him out of the house and he has to spend Christmas alone. (S26 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Proposal Proposal: Amy must decide whether or not to marry Sheldon and gives him an answer to his proposal. Howard and Bernadette struggle with some unexpected news. (S11 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Retraction Reaction: Leonard angers the university during an embarrassing interview. Amy and Bernadette must hide their success from Sheldon and Howard. (S11 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gone Boy: Bart falls into an old top-secret underground military installation in the woods. (S29 Ep9/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: 'Tis the 30th Season: After a terrible Black Friday when Marge can't buy the right gifts, can the Simpsons have a relaxing Christmas in Florida? (S30 Ep10/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Conjugal Configuration: Sheldon and Amy's honeymoon runs aground, while Penny and Leonard discover that they are uncomfortably similar to Amy's parents. (S12 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Wedding Gift Wormhole: A stressed Sheldon and Amy struggle to work out what the 'perfect gift' is that Leonard and Penny gave them on their wedding day. (S12 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Procreation Calculation: Stuart starts bringing his new girlfriend home to Howard and Bernadette's house. Penny and Leonard talk about starting a family. (S12 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tam Turbulence: When Sheldon won't tell anyone why he's never mentioned Tam, his childhood best friend, Leonard tries to find out more. (S12 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Planetarium Collision: Sheldon accidentally sabotages Amy's career. Raj isn't keen when Howard's invited to host a show with him at the planetarium. (S12 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Imitation Perturbation: Howard dresses up as Sheldon for Halloween, so Sheldon gets revenge. Leonard is shocked that Penny can't recall their first kiss. (S12 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Grant Allocation Derivation: Leonard is made responsible for distributing extra grant money. Bernadette turns the garden playhouse into a hideaway to escape her family. (S12 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Consummation Deviation: Sheldon aims to bond with Amy's father, but Howard lures Mr Fowler away with his magic tricks. Raj and Anu try to get physical. (S12 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Citation Negation: Sheldon and Amy get some devastating news. Bernadette asks Stuart's girlfriend Denise to teach her how to beat Howard at a video game. (S12 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The VCR Illumination: Sheldon and Amy are still upset about their theory being disproven, but a video tape from Sheldon's past inspires him not to give up. (S12 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Paintball Scattering: Jealousy, trust issues and tension among the couples in the gang cause mayhem when Penny and Leonard organise a paintball game. (S12 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Propagation Proposition: Penny's ex-boyfriend Zack and his wife want a baby, but when they encounter fertility problems, they ask Leonard for his help. (S12 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Confirmation Polarization: Sheldon and Amy are thrilled when their super-asymmetry theory is proved correct. Bernadette enjoys some big success at work. (S12 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Meteorite Manifestation: Sheldon is thrilled to help Howard and Bernadette with some bureaucratic paperwork, until he realises that they're breaking the law. (S12 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Donation Oscillation: Penny attempts to sabotage Leonard's efforts to help her ex-boyfriend Zack and his wife Marissa have a family of their own. (S12 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The D & D Vortex: When the gang find out that Wil Wheaton is hosting a celebrity game of Dungeons & Dragons at his home, deception and betrayal take hold. (S12 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Conference Valuation: Penny and Bernadette go to San Diego for a sales convention, leaving Howard in charge of Michael and Halley while they're away. (S12 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Laureate Accumulation: When their academic competitors charm America on a publicity tour, Sheldon and Amy try to get some Nobel laureates on their side. (S12 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Inspiration Deprivation: Amy has a meltdown when she feels the pressure of what it would mean for women everywhere if she were to win a Nobel Prize. (S12 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Decision Reverberation: Raj publishes a paper that suggests he may have discovered alien life. Penny encourages Leonard to stand up for himself. (S12 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Plagiarism Schism: Barry Kripke finds proof that Dr Pemberton plagiarised his thesis in college. Should Sheldon and Amy turn in their rival? (S12 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Maternal Conclusion: Leonard is surprised when his mother Beverly comes to visit and is kind to him, until he finds out the real reason she's there. (S12 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Change Constant: Sheldon and Amy stay up late awaiting a phone call that could bring big news from the Nobel Committee: are their lives about to change? (S12 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Stockholm Syndrome: Howard and Bernadette go on a trip without their children, Leonard and Penny try to keep a secret, and Raj makes a new friend. (S12 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Saddlesore Galactica: Homer and Bart save a horse from the fair and decide to train him as an American footballer. Or maybe a racehorse. (S11 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: I Won't Be Home for Christmas: When Moe convinces Homer to stay out late on Christmas Eve, Marge kicks him out of the house and he has to spend Christmas alone. (S26 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gone Boy: Bart falls into an old top-secret underground military installation in the woods. (S29 Ep9/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: 'Tis the 30th Season: After a terrible Black Friday when Marge can't buy the right gifts, can the Simpsons have a relaxing Christmas in Florida? (S30 Ep10/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox Festive Special
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's favourite armchair critics review 2024's Christmas TV, from Strictly to Gavin & Stacey, First Dates, Hot Frosty, Bullseye, The Dog House, Is It Cake? and Fanny Cradock. (S24 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Inbetweeners
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Fashion Show: It's the start of term and Carli is organising a charity fashion show. It's only for the cool kids, so our heroes aren't involved - until a last-minute hitch. (S3 Ep1/6)

Film4.uk.title: Wrath of Man
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Jason Statham reunites with director Guy Ritchie to give it both barrels as a mysterious hardman working for a money truck firm that keeps getting hit. But is he an inside man?

Film4.uk.title: Sexy Beast
Film4.uk.description: (2000) Jonathan Glazer's thriller with Ray Winstone, Ben Kingsley and Ian McShane. A criminal's blissful retirment is shattered by a psychopathic gangster who insists on one more job.

Film4.uk.title: Hue & Cry
Film4.uk.description: (1947) The very first Ealing comedy is set in the post-war East End. A boy tries to catch a gang of thieves who are using his favourite comic to communicate their dastardly deeds.

Film4.uk.title: Monster House
Film4.uk.description: (2006) Spooky animated caper with Maggie Gyllenhaal and Steve Buscemi. A young boy and his babysitter spy on the creepy neighbour. Did he really eat his wife?

Film4.uk.description: (1994) Festive family drama. Richard Attenborough stars as a department store Santa who insists he's the real Santa Claus. But can he prove it in court?

Film4.uk.title: Evolution
Film4.uk.description: (2001) Scary sci-fi comedy. Can David Duchovny, Julianne Moore and Orlando Jones save humanity from a rapidly evolving, predatory alien species? Well, DD used to be Fox Mulder, so...

Film4.uk.title: Cowboys & Aliens
Film4.uk.description: (2011) Sci-fi western starring Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford. A brutal cattle baron and his amnesiac enemy must cease their feuding when a town is attacked by aliens.

Film4.uk.title: Mrs Harris Goes to Paris
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Lesley Manville stars as a cleaner who saves up and heads to Paris to get herself a Dior couture dress, in director Anthony Fabian's fabulous, Oscar-nominated period comedy drama.

Film4.uk.title: The Invitation
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Gothic horror with Nathalie Emmanuel. A struggling New York artist discovers she has rich British relatives and accepts an invitation to a wedding in Whitby. Well, blood is blood.

Film4.uk.title: Step Brothers
Film4.uk.description: (2008) Outrageous comedy with Will Ferrell and John C. Reilly. When two 40-year-old man-children's parents marry, can the lads settle their differences and grow up? Strong language/nudity.

Film4.uk.title: Anastasia
Film4.uk.description: (1956) Historical drama. The Oscar-winning Ingrid Bergman stars as an amnesiac refugee who Yul Brynner tries to pass off as the daughter of the murdered Tsar of Russia, Nicholas II.

Film4.uk.title: The Muppets Take Manhattan
Film4.uk.description: (1984) It's time to put on make-up. It's time to light the lights. Kermit, Miss Piggy, Fozzy, the Blues one and the gang embark on a musical adventure as they try to make it on Broadway.

Film4.uk.description: (1996) Brian Levant's festive all-action comedy. Arnold Schwarzenegger is on a mission to get his son (Jake Lloyd) the must-have Christmas toy, Turbo Man. But it's sold out everywhere...

Film4.uk.title: Tooth Fairy
Film4.uk.description: (2010) Family fantasy comedy. Dwayne Johnson stars as a tough ice hockey player who is transformed into a real-life fairy as punishment for telling a child that tooth fairies don't exist.

Film4.uk.title: The Devil Wears Prada
Film4.uk.description: (2006) Comedy-drama starring Anne Hathaway and Meryl Streep. A naive young woman lands a job as assistant to one of New York's most important, but ruthless and cynical, magazine editors.

Film4.uk.title: The Equalizer
Film4.uk.description: (2014) Thriller. Denzel Washington stars as an ex-soldier who comes out of retirement to help a teenage sex worker who's been assaulted by her pimp.

UAndW.uk.description: There's a major rescue operation on the M1 after a car towing a caravan rolls over and hits a lamp post - trapping the driver. A teacher out on his mountain bike suffers a brain injury. S5 Ep2

UAndW.uk.title: 999 Rescue Squad
UAndW.uk.description: The team helps a biker critically injured in a crash, and a man vanishes after going for a swim in a Pennines lake, sparking a major rescue operation. S5 Ep3

UAndW.uk.title: 999 Rescue Squad
UAndW.uk.description: A dangerous driver in a pick-up truck causes carnage when his vehicle rolls over and the HART team are called to free him and his passenger from the wreckage. S5 Ep4

UAndW.uk.title: 999 Rescue Squad
UAndW.uk.description: A hitman linked to a drugs gang guns down two men in a supermarket car park. Later, a teenage dare leads to a massive rescue operation after a boy vanishes in the water. S5 Ep5

UAndW.uk.title: 999 Rescue Squad
